## Remote Control Device [/devices/{did}]

+ Parameters
    + did (required, string, `abadc`)
    
### Set Data to Device [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Header
        
            X-Gizwits-Application-Id: {appid}
            
    + Body
        
            {
                "data": [{
                    "attr": "abc",
                    "val": 1
                }]
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
